Title: Anny - en gatepiges roman
Actors: Julie Jansen-Fuhr, Johan Andersson, Gunlaug Lund
Plot: Anny works in a cigar-shop. Wholesaler Willmann fancy Anny and hire her as his housemaid. Soon the two have an intimate relationship. But Anny finds someone new. At a carnival. Her next step is to get Willman's son to get to his father's safe. Together they steal the family's fortune and have a great time doing away with all of it. Anny sink deeper and deeper in misery.
